      </answers>
      <UID>8720</UID>
    </dlgPart>
    <dlgPart>
      <portrait />
      <speaker_name />
      <npc_text>“Certainly,” nods the man. “You can pray and light a candle. The Gods will bless you for it.”</npc_text>
      <onLoadScripts />
      <answers>
        <dlgAnsw>
          <text>“So you maintain these machines?”</text>
