    </dlgPart>
    <dlgPart>
      <portrait />
      <speaker_name />
      <npc_text>“I’m only a novice,” says the man. “We look after the elders and the elders look after the machines. The elders shut themselves off from the world and live in darkness to be closer to the Gods.”</npc_text>
      <onLoadScripts />
      <answers>
        <dlgAnsw>
          <text>“How does it get them closer to the Gods?”</text>
          <def_link>8723</def_link>
          <checkOnAppear />
          <checksOnClick />
          <linksOnClick />
          <scriptsOnClick />
        </dlgAnsw>
      </answers>
      <UID>8722</UID>
    </dlgPart>
    <dlgPart>
      <portrait />
      <speaker_name />
      <npc_text>“Only an empty vessel can be filled,” says the man with dead certainty. “You must empty your mind from all earthly thoughts to hear the Gods when they talk to you. It takes years just to prepare yourself for the transition.”</npc_text>
      <onLoadScripts />
      <answers>
        <dlgAnsw>
          <text>“The transition?”</text>
          <def_link>8724</def_link>
          <checkOnAppear />
          <checksOnClick />
          <linksOnClick />
          <scriptsOnClick />
        </dlgAnsw>
      </answers>
      <UID>8723</UID>
    </dlgPart>
    <dlgPart>
      <portrait />
      <speaker_name />
      <npc_text>“When the novice is ready, he dedicates his life to the Gods and descends into darkness, leaving the world behind. From this day forward, he spends his days in meditation and prayer,” he says wistfully. “No more work.”</npc_text>
      <onLoadScripts />
      <answers>
        <dlgAnsw>
          <text>“So that’s your retirement plan? Become an elder and live the life of leisure in the darkness?”</text>
          <def_link>8725</def_link>
          <checkOnAppear />
          <checksOnClick />
          <linksOnClick />
          <scriptsOnClick />
        </dlgAnsw>
      </answers>
      <UID>8724</UID>
